{"id":62281,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/【图集】冰岛火山爆发，火山灰扰乱欧洲/","date":"2010-04-30T08:30:54Z","modified":"2010-04-30T08:30:54Z","title":"【图集】冰岛火山爆发，火山灰扰乱欧洲","content":"<div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"> </div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;;font-size:large\"><b>原文标题：</b></span><span style=\"font-size:large\"><a href=\"http://www.lexpress.fr/diaporama/diapo-photo/actualite/monde/eruption-et-nuage-de-cendres-en-islande_885222.html\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana\"><span style=\"color:blue\"><u><b>Eruption en Islande, nuage de cendres sur l&#8217;Europe</b></u></span></span></span></a></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;;font-size:large\"><b>译文标题：Lex：冰岛火山爆发，火山灰云团扰乱欧洲 </b></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">作者：不详（</span><a href=\"http://www.lexpress.fr/\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:blue\"><u>www.lexpress.fr/</u></span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">）</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">发表时间：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"> 2010-04-16 11:04:00       </span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">更新时间：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">2010-04-21 12:00:00</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">译者： 木木</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><i><b style=\"color:red\">注：因博客显示限制，完整图片请查阅<a href=\"https://yyii.org/tu/\">译图</a>博客。 </b></i></span></span></div>\n<div><b><br /></b></div>\n<div><b><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">冰岛南部的火山爆发产生大面积火山灰云团，在风力和风向等因素影响下，造成欧洲航空交通瘫痪。 </span></b></div>\n<div><b><br /></b></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_27dk97ghdk_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">艾雅法拉火山（冰岛语</span><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Eyjafjallaj%C3%B6kull.ogg\"><span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:blue\"><u>发音</u></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">）的喷发还在继续。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_28zx52svdg_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">火山爆发之后的火山灰云团已经扩散了将近一个星期，造成了欧洲地区航空交通的瘫痪。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_29pmfs97f7_b\" style=\"height:390px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">火山开始先喷发熔岩，常年被冰川覆盖的火山在喷发时，炽热的岩浆首先遇上含水量巨大的冰川，温度上剧烈的反差制造出大量的水蒸汽，而火山熔岩就在这一过程中被分解成纹理细密的火山灰，在强大的推力下喷射向高空，进而覆盖向整个欧洲。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_306cp25mcm_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">气象预报预测未来几天，在火山区的低海拔地区会受到微弱的风力影响，周末有降雨。但是在高海拔地区，冰岛上空的强风将吹往欧洲方向。火山灰柱的高度能达到强风的临界高度吗<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">?</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_31dnzq5rg3_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">火山上空暴风雨交加<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">&#8230;&#8230;</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_32s2v3t4cf_b\" style=\"height:378px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">艾雅法拉火山位于冰岛南部的冰川顶端，图为周三，火山爆发前夕的上午。此次火山爆发引起了该地区数次强烈地震。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_33x9vzffdn_b\" style=\"height:377px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">虽然覆盖向东南方向的火山灰云团造成了整个欧洲空中交通的混乱，但是冰岛的天空依然明朗，几乎没有受到影响。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_34jvnfpcfn_b\" style=\"height:419px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">冰岛专家表示，上周三冰岛火山爆发以来，火山灰柱已经明显减小。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_35d47c7xfx_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/monde/europe/mais-ou-se-trouve-donc-ce-nuage_885199.html\"><span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:blue\"><u>火山灰云团</u></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">已经上升到了冰岛南部的高空。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_36g53hcchq_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">火山喷出的大量烟尘和熔岩碎屑会破坏飞机控制系统，使引擎失灵，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">许多</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">欧洲</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">国家当局采取预防措施，关闭了机场运营。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_37ptzfc5cf_b\" style=\"height:476px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">在卫星上拍摄的，风力影响下向东南方推进的火山灰云团。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_38f32zttdm_b\" style=\"height:486px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">矛盾的是，冰岛却幸免于航空交通的危害，火山灰都涌向了东南部和欧洲大陆。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_39hnm63ncw_b\" style=\"height:393px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">巨大的火山灰造成北欧的大部分飞机停飞，导致法国、英国、荷兰、比利时、挪威、丹麦和瑞典等国纷纷关闭了领空。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_40drknvfgf_b\" style=\"height:422px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">由于冰岛南部形成了大量火山灰云团，多个国家的航班受到严重影响。目前</span><a href=\"http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/monde/aucun-avion-au-depart-de-paris-jusqu-au-moins-14h_885179.html\"><span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:blue\"><u>法国</u></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">、冰岛、挪威、瑞典、俄罗斯、英国等欧洲西北部国家的机场运营均受到阻碍，航班或取消或延误，美国也已经下令停飞跨大西洋的多数航班。 </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_41c89pgsfb_b\" style=\"height:417px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">由于欧洲大部分领空被关闭，从惠灵顿到东京，途经香港和新加坡的数千的乘客，对于众多取消和延误的航班都还在未知中等待。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_42hpdnhsg6_b\" style=\"height:400px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">专家强调火山喷发可能会持续至少几个星期，所以机场的关闭还将继续下去。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_43rcg8s6dt_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">回到冰岛，冰川上都被火山灰覆盖。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_44gx5q9vdx_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">火山灰、土、碎冰块在地上混杂在一起。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_45hh75wshn_b\" style=\"height:404px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">火山灰流入了冰川融水<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">&#8230;&#8230;</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_46g3kkb8dm_b\" style=\"height:404px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">&#8230;&#8230;<span>汇入北大西洋。</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_47jdv7rdd_b\" style=\"height:390px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：法新社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">火山爆发产生的洪流可能会加剧艾雅法拉冰川的融化，并且有专家担心，冰岛不到一个月内将会有第二次火山爆发。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_48cbhmvvgj_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">冰川被火山灰覆盖。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_49hmrx3ng4_b\" style=\"height:403px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">冰川被火山灰覆盖。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_50dqd2zgc2_b\" style=\"height:393px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：路透社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">由于火山爆发引发洪水，冰岛当局已经于星期四疏散了附近近百居民。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dgwpvz94_51fjxcrrjb_b\" style=\"height:402px;width:605px\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:#acacac\">照片来源：法新社</span></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">房屋和桥梁的破坏程度也都显示了灾难的严重。</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family:&#39;verdana&#39;\"><span style=\"color:black\">来源说明：本文<span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">1.0</span><span>版本来源译者的志愿翻译者团队。</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;verdana&#39;\"><span style=\"color:black\">收录说明：本文已经收录到<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span><span>译者文集</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span><span>中，同时进入</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span><span>最新消息</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span><span>、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span><span>译者频道</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">看世界</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span><span>、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">零星其他</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span><span>、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">“</span><span>译者<span style=\"font-family:Verdana\">木木</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana\"></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">”</span><span>、“译图”索引。</span></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><br /></span> </div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;;font-size:x-small\"><i>©<span>译者遵守</span></i></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/2.5/cn/\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"color:blue\"><u><i>CC<span>协议</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2.5</span></i></u></span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;;font-size:x-small\"><i>您可以自由复制、发行、展览、表演、放映、广播或通过信息网络传播，创作演绎本作品。惟须遵守下列条件：署名，非商业性使用，相同方式共享。</i></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-3003014144404406234?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\"></div>\n","author":141,"categories":[1],"tags":[5908,8840]}